OL,3,C'No one beyond scrutiny': Parliament
OL,4,Cto release of documents on Andrew's
OL,5,Crole
OL,7,FIt came after a cache of emails
OL,8,Freleased by the US Department of
OL,9,FJustice, which appeared to show the
OL,10,Fformer duke sharing reports of
OL,11,Fofficial visits to Hong Kong, Vietnam,
OL,12,Fand Singapore with the convicted
OL,13,Fpaedophile.
OL,15,FAndrew has consistently denied any
OL,16,Fwrongdoing relating to Epstein.
OL,18,FThe Liberal Democrats introduced the
OL,19,Fmotion via a parliamentary procedure
OL,20,Fcalled a 'humble address'.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
