OL,3,C'No one beyond scrutiny': Parliament
OL,4,Cto release of documents on Andrew's
OL,5,Crole
OL,7,FThe Liberal Democrats motion called
OL,8,Ffor the government to "lay before the
OL,9,Fhouse all papers relating to the
OL,10,Fcreation of the role of special
OL,11,Frepresentative for trade and
OL,12,Finvestment and Andrew Mountbatten-
OL,13,FWindsor's appointment to that role".
OL,15,FIt also specified that documents which
OL,16,Fmight detail any advice given by Peter
OL,17,FMandelson to then Prime Minister about
OL,18,Fthe "suitability of Andrew Mountbatten-
OL,19,FWindsor for the appointment".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
