PN,30511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1771959890
OL,3,C'No one beyond scrutiny': Parliament
OL,4,Cto release of documents on Andrew's
OL,5,Crole
OL,7,FWatch: Lord Mandelson was escorted out
OL,8,Fof his house in Camden on Monday by a
OL,9,Fplain clothes police officer.
OL,11,FSir Ed Davey said: "The public is
OL,12,Frightly demanding to know how Andrew
OL,13,FMountbatten-Windsor was appointed to
OL,14,Frepresent our nation in a high-level
OL,15,Ftrade role. The Liberal Democrats are
OL,16,Fmoving a binding motion to force the
OL,17,FGovernment to come clean."
OL,26,@sD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1771959890
OL,3,C'No one beyond scrutiny': Parliament
OL,4,Cto release of documents on Andrew's
OL,5,Crole
OL,7,F"We need to see the vetting files, the
OL,8,Fdue diligence reports, and the
OL,9,Fcorrespondence to understand how this
OL,10,Fappointment came to be, and whether
OL,11,Fglaring warning signs were missed," he
OL,12,Fsaid in a statement.
OL,14,F"There's also a much broader principle
OL,15,Fat stake here. No one, regardless of
OL,16,Ftheir title or their friends, should
OL,17,Fbe beyond the scrutiny of Parliament."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
