OL,3,C'No one beyond scrutiny': Parliament
OL,4,Cto release of documents on Andrew's
OL,5,Crole
OL,7,FSpeaking last week, the Committee's
OL,8,Fchair Liam Byrne, who is also Labour
OL,9,FMP for Birmingham Hodge Hill and
OL,10,FSolihull North, said "nothing is off
OL,11,Fthe table" in terms of what his
OL,12,Fcommittee might decide to do.
OL,14,F"This is something we're going to take
OL,15,Facutely seriously, and I can guarantee
OL,16,Fyou that MPs are not in the market for
OL,17,Fletting anything slip through the
OL,18,Fcracks," he said.
OL,26,@vD@AOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
